@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="page-header reveal">
    <div>
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">Last updated: June 21, 2026</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card reveal" style="max-width:850px; margin:0 auto; padding:2.5rem; line-height:1.8;">
    <h2 style="font-size:1.3rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--accent-light); margin-bottom:1rem;">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Welcome to JobBoard. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website, apply for jobs, or use our messaging features.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.3rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--accent-light); margin-bottom:1rem;">2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom:1rem;">
        We collect personal details that you voluntarily provide to us when registering, posting listings, or applying for jobs. This information includes:
    </p>
    <ul style="color:var(--text-secondary); padding-left:1.5rem; margin-bottom:2rem; list-style-type:disc;">
        <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;"><strong>Account Info:</strong> Name, email address, password, company details, and creation dates.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;"><strong>Candidate Materials:</strong> Cover letters, resumes/CV files (PDF or DOCX format) uploaded during applications.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;"><strong>Communications:</strong> Message contents sent via our built-in chatting and mini-chat drawer widget.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.3rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--accent-light); margin-bottom:1rem;">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom:1rem;">
        We use the information we collect to facilitate the employment match-making process, including:
    </p>
    <ul style="color:var(--text-secondary); padding-left:1.5rem; margin-bottom:2rem; list-style-type:disc;">
        <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Managing and authenticating your account.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Allowing employers to view applications, cover letters, and download candidate CV files.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Providing real-time notifications and delivering chat messages between employers and candidates.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Maintaining security and preventing fraudulent job listings or spam.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.3rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--accent-light); margin-bottom:1rem;">4. Storage & File Security</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Uploaded CV files are stored securely on our web hosting server. Resumes are capped at a maximum size of 1MB and restricted to PDF and DOCX extensions to prevent malicious code execution. We only share candidate CV files and application details with the specific Employer who posted the job listing.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.3rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--accent-light); margin-bottom:1rem;">5. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom:2rem;">
        We use cookies to maintain your active authentication session and store login state. These cookies do not contain personal tracking data and are essential for cookie-based Identity authentication.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.3rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--accent-light); margin-bottom:1rem;">6. Contact Us</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
        If you have any questions or concerns regarding our Privacy Policy or data handling practices, feel free to reach out to us:
    </p>
    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);">
        ✉️ Email: privacy@jobboard.com <br/>
        📞 Phone: +1 (555) 019-2834
    </p>
</div>
